name: bimbostyleTwo  - LORA
description:
This model basically bimbofies your generated girls (not that extreme) it's a blend of different insta models.

On lower setting it's great to increase the breast size and make the model fit.

Trained on rev_11

The pictures are a 0.1 increase starting at 0.1 on the same batch witch same starting seed ending in 1.

Also if you want to mix my models, i would recommend to always put the stronger weighted Lora in the front. i.e.

<lora:bimbostyleThree:0.5>:<lora:bimbostyleTwo:0.3>

And, at least for me, going over a total strength of 1 would result in heavy artefacts (sweetspot round .75-.85)
